data.description: This beautiful ranch home has 3-bedroom, 1 bathroom located close to Lake Erie. Updated kitchen cabinets, hardwood floors and a nice fireplace. Has potential to make a 4th bedroom.  Spacious backyard to play or entertain. Mold remediation will be completed in the crawlspace prior to closing. Few blocks away from Overlook Beach Park.
